  <entry>
    <title>leecode2两数相加</title>
    <url>/2021/05/14/leecode/%E4%B8%A4%E6%95%B0%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="吐槽"><a href="#吐槽" class="headerlink" title="吐槽"></a>吐槽</h3><p>好了，同学们，我破防了，我**，这题目怎末就如此恶心呢？我终于明白了为啥这些师哥在毕业的时候都头发那么少了，呜呜呜。学习算法不难，难的是自己设计算法以及用所学的知识去解决具体的问题。。。。</p>
<h3 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h3><p>好吧，我还没想好如何去描述这题的思路，下次更新的时候补上。嘿嘿🤭</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="代"><a href="#代" class="headerlink" title="代"></a>代</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * Definition for singly-linked list.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * struct ListNode &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> *     int val;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> *     struct ListNode *next;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> * &#125;;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">struct ListNode* <span class="title">addTwoNumbers</span><span class="params">(struct ListNode* l1, struct ListNode* l2)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">nl1</span> =</span> l1;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">nl2</span> =</span> l2;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">l3</span> =</span> (struct ListNode*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">    l3-&gt;next = <span class="literal">NULL</span>; <span class="comment">//不加这个会出错，next未为空</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">ListNode</span>* <span class="title">nl3</span> =</span> l3;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(l3 == <span class="literal">NULL</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">-1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> carry = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    nl3-&gt;val = (nl1-&gt;val + nl2-&gt;val + carry)%<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    carry = (nl1-&gt;val + nl2-&gt;val + carry)/<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(nl1-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span> &amp;&amp; nl2-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        nl1 = nl1-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl2 = nl2-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;next = (struct ListNode*)<span class="built_in">calloc</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;val = (nl1-&gt;val + nl2-&gt;val + carry)%<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        carry = (nl1-&gt;val + nl2-&gt;val + carry)/<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(nl1-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        nl1=nl1-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;next = (struct ListNode*)<span class="built_in">calloc</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;val = (nl1-&gt;val + carry)%<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        carry = (nl1-&gt;val + carry)/<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(nl2-&gt;next != <span class="literal">NULL</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        nl2=nl2-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;next = (struct ListNode*)<span class="built_in">calloc</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;val = (nl2-&gt;val + carry)%<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        carry = (nl2-&gt;val + carry)/<span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(carry != <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;next = (struct ListNode*)<span class="built_in">calloc</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(struct ListNode));</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3-&gt;val = carry;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">free</span>(nl3);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = nl3-&gt;next;</span><br><span class="line">        nl3 = <span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">free</span>(nl3);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> l3;</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
